00:01:03.922 --> 00:01:06.521
postwar socialist country

00:01:06.522 --> 00:01:07.321
that

00:01:07.322 --> 00:01:11.841
probably just got rid of feudalism and started trying to do socialism

00:01:11.842 --> 00:01:15.201
with anyone in Europe or the United States.

